               <p>Third Count. Stood charged for that he, being in the same dwelling-house, did feloniously steal a Bill of Exchange, value 434 l. 14 s. the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050109-14-victim170" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Loosely
